description: Template for feature MODULE_DOC.md under src/features
alwaysApply: false
---

# Module: <feature-name>


**Short:** One-line summary.


**Purpose:** Business intent (e.g. "Stream and persist market data subscriptions for instruments").


**Layout (this repo):**

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `<feature>.module.ts` | Nest module definition & imports |
| `application/` | Application services, orchestration, scheduled jobs |
| `domain/` | Entities, domain types |
| `infra/` | Outbound adapters (providers, queues, external APIs) |
| `interface/` | Controllers, gateways, `dto/` |
| `MODULE_DOC.md` | This document |
| `*.spec.ts` / `__tests__/` | Unit and integration tests |
| `*.md` (optional) | Flow docs, architecture notes |


**Flow diagram:** `flowcharts/<feature>-flow.svg` or Mermaid in this file


**Dependencies:** Other `src/features/*`, `src/shared/*`, `src/infra/*`, external APIs


**APIs:**

- REST: method, path, brief purpose
- WebSocket: event names, payload summary (if any)


**Env vars:**

- `<FEATURE>_ENABLED=true`
- `<FEATURE>_SETTING=...`


**Tests:** Coverage expectations; when to run integration / Testcontainers


**Change-log:** (update on each meaningful change — date + summary)
